DarkMouse:
She looked at Galvatron. "Oh, well, sure. Ok then. Fine. I can do 
that."  She turned and looked at the wall for a moment. She was 
seeing herself once again going on a suicide run. Just like the one 
she and Quickstrike when on that day before she was killed and 
brought back.  She sighed and wished she could just stay in the ship. 
But then again, she had her orders and she couldn't turn them down.  
She regained her smart tailed smile and grabbed her weapon. "OK then. 
let's get a move on. I want to get back in time to watch General 
Repair Bay on the monitor."
